PrecisOrder fixing WEDNESDAY, JULY 5, 2000 as the day upon which different provisions of this Act [BILL C-22 - Proceeds of Crime (Money Laundering) Act], being chapter 17 of the Statutes of Canada, 2000, shall COME INTO FORCE, thus establishing an independent agency called the FINANCIAL TRANSACTIONS AND REPORTS ANALYSIS CENTRE OF CANADA.

precis:
Order fixing WEDNESDAY, JULY 5, 2000 as the day upon which different
provisions of this Act [BILL C-22 - Proceeds of Crime (Money Laundering)
Act], being chapter 17 of the Statutes of Canada, 2000, shall COME INTO
FORCE, thus establishing an independent agency called the FINANCIAL
TRANSACTIONS AND REPORTS ANALYSIS CENTRE OF CANADA.
